  "id": "RAW_b9f71546",
  "title": "马斯克与 OpenAI 庭审中真正重要（或应该重要）的事",
  "url": "https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/what-matters-or-should-matter-at",
  "date": "2026-05-05 20:56:51",
  "author": "Gary Marcus",
  "siteName": "Marcus on AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_48d794f8-265a-44d6-b3a4-01357f027538_1178x335.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_48d794f8-265a-44d6-b3a4-01357f027538_1178x335.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_48d794f8-265a-44d6-b3a4-01357f027538_1178x335.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_48d794f8-265a-44d6-b3a4-01357f027538_1178x335.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_48d794f8-265a-44d6-b3a4-01357f027538_1178x335.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d682179c-a5f6-4405-849f-4cad4a1dc200/public\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/48d794f8-265a-44d6-b3a4-01357f027538_1178x335.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:335,&quot;width&quot;:1178,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:84146,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/196586628?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48d794f8-265a-44d6-b3a4-01357f027538_1178x335.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_48d794f8-265a-44d6-b3a4-01357f027538_1178x335.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_48d794f8-265a-44d6-b3a4-01357f027538_1178x335.png 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5f518bfd-e264-4f8b-310a-dab428e89200/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d682179c-a5f6-4405-849f-4cad4a1dc200/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>I don’t know what’s going to happen; it’s a jury trial. And it’s very far from over.</p>\n   <p><span>One view is that for all the drama nothing much has happened so far. A few minutes ago Jeremy Kahn from </span><em>Fortune</em><span> represented that view in </span><a href=\"https://view.mail.fortune.com/?vawpToken=TXBAXIUZUEUEDAR75SD2X246HM.130013&amp;utm_source=sfmc&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=NL_eye-on-ai_2026-5-5_114813&amp;utm_term=eye-on-ai&amp;sfmc_id=16024901\">his newsletter</a><span>:</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d9723b5d-bc78-4fe7-51a9-c3e2d3dc4900/public\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_347825f9-200c-4fa3-b010-453af8306d7e_1000x1041.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_347825f9-200c-4fa3-b010-453af8306d7e_1000x1041.png 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8bb974e0-89e0-4ddd-a29c-2039daca9a00/public 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_347825f9-200c-4fa3-b010-453af8306d7e_1000x1041.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_347825f9-200c-4fa3-b010-453af8306d7e_1000x1041.png\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/347825f9-200c-4fa3-b010-453af8306d7e_1000x1041.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1041,&quot;width&quot;:1000,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:167909,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/196586628?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F347825f9-200c-4fa3-b010-453af8306d7e_1000x1041.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dcfbd349-e46c-4dd6-7ae7-94b5fae22f00/public 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_347825f9-200c-4fa3-b010-453af8306d7e_1000x1041.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_347825f9-200c-4fa3-b010-453af8306d7e_1000x1041.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_347825f9-200c-4fa3-b010-453af8306d7e_1000x1041.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>On Kahn’s telling, “Most legal analysts say Musk’s case is weak and that he’s likely to lose. In fact, I’m surprised the case has even come to trial.”</p>\n   <p>But few knew what secrets were contained in OpenAI cofounder Greg Brockman’s diary,, and yesterday and today mostly centered on them. Kahn sums up some of revelations, and in my view they don’t look good:</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214254_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1006,&quot;width&quot;:1345,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:243757,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/196586628?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbdc97b84-2cb1-4272-9086-37a51a57d40e_1345x1006.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ebed2d55-55b1-4b33-bbf2-2421b8320f50_1345x1006.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>A fairly widely-followed blogger on X was </span><a href=\"https://x.com/ns123abc/status/2051534855263912433?s=61\">withering.</a><span> arguing that Brockman basically vindicated Musk’s critique, beat by beat:</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5bf4edb3-fa12-4625-93b1-8c819c5cd400/public\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1373,&quot;width&quot;:1132,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1519662,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/196586628?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_02500ffa-9829-425a-8171-219361fb63e7_1132x1373.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>In my view, by vividly explaining how he deceived Musk about his commitment to the nonprofit, without a trace of remorse, OpenAI’s Brockman has done Musk’s counsel a huge favor.</p>\n   <p>§</p>\n   <p><span>So much so that yesterday there were a </span><em>lot</em><span> of jokes about Brockman’s diary:</span></p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/alexeheath/status/2051435261972853247?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/alexeheath/status/2051435261972853247?s=61&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;takeaway from Greg Brockman testimony at Elon vs. OpenAI trial today is that no grown man should have a diary&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;alexeheath&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Alex Heath&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/1983378648787988480/cGjEMRvw_normal.jpg&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2026-05-04T22:54:14.000Z&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;reply_count&quot;:58,&quot;retweet_count&quot;:39,&quot;like_count&quot;:1579,&quot;impression_count&quot;:119967,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <di