le=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">takeaway from Greg Brockman testimony at Elon vs. OpenAI trial today is that no grown man should have a diary</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">10:54 PM · May 4, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">120K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">58 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">39 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">1.58K Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p>and</p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/garyfung/status/2049997538632372690?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/garyfung/status/2049997538632372690?s=61&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;Sam to Greg on the ClosedAI plot:\\n\\nmind not to write our grifts down in email?&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;garyfung&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;gary IH fung&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/1110680015409053696/ruAbyYmJ_normal.png&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2026-04-30T23:41:14.000Z&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[{&quot;img_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/media/HHMN5bCbEAAvHJ8.jpg&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;https://t.co/9dOxVGuDu6&quot;}],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;🚨 Musk's lawyers just showed the jury the most damaging document in evidence on Brockman:\\n\\nNovember 2017 Brockman writes in his private diary:\\n\\n&amp;gt;\\&quot;the true answer is that we want [musk] out... if three months later we're doing b-corp then it was a lie\\&quot;\\n&amp;gt;“can’t see us turning this&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;ns123abc&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;NIK&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/2048822563821035520/7nxCFEnk_normal.jpg&quot;},&quot;reply_count&quot;:1,&quot;retweet_count&quot;:2,&quot;like_count&quot;:10,&quot;impression_count&quot;:14778,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n       <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n        <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ruAbyYmJ.png 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ruAbyYmJ.png 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ruAbyYmJ.png 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ruAbyYmJ.png\" alt=\"X avatar for @garyfung\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ruAbyYmJ.png 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ruAbyYmJ.png 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_ruAbyYmJ.png 3x\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">gary IH fung</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@garyfung</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n       <g>\n        <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">Sam to Greg on the ClosedAI plot: mind not to write our grifts down in email?</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset bg-black-dCpgGg outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 container-aGHQ9p\">\n      <img src=\"https://pbs.substack.com/media/HHMN5bCbEAAvHJ8.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"image-c_FmAR\">\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset elevatedTheme-fBklGV\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-padding-12 pc-boxShadow-none pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm sizing-border-box-DggLA4\">\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-8 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n        <div style=\"--scale:20px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-20 pc-height-20 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n         <div style=\"--scale:20px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-20 pc-height-20 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n          <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_7nxCFEnk.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_7nxCFEnk.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_7nxCFEnk.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_7nxCFEnk.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @ns123abc\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_7nxCFEnk.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_7nxCFEnk.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_7nxCFEnk.jpg 3x\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">NIK</span> <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@ns123abc</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">🚨 Musk's lawyers just showed the jury the most damaging document in evidence on Brockman: November 2017 Brockman writes in his private diary: &gt;\"the true answer is that we want [musk] out... if three months later we're doing b-corp then it was a lie\" &gt;“can’t see us turning this</div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">11:41 PM · Apr 30, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">14.8K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">1 Reply</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">2 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">10 Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p>§</p>\n   <p><span>The trial is far from over; more witnesses are expected, including Satya Nadella and Sam Altman, as well as </span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shivon_Zilis\">Shivon Zilis</a><span>, former OpenAI board member and mother of 4 of Elon’s children, and former OpenAI CTO Mira Murati.</span></p>\n   <p>And it’s a jury trial, so who knows what will happen.</p>\n   <p>OpenAI’s counsel will continue to emphasize Musk’s character flaws; Musk’s counsel will continue to harp on OpenAI deceit. Nobody will come off well.</p>\n   <p>But here’s what I (a fan neither of Musk nor OpenAI) think it boils down to:</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_71b078ab-86d7-4aea-966e-28d6585a2b7a_1160x433.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_71b078ab-86d7-4aea-966e-28d6585a2b7a_1160x433.png 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7b21bd16-bb8f-4fd8-f207-34d5f516ec00/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214254_71b078ab-86d7-4aea-966e-28d6585a2b7a_1160x433.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_71b078ab-86d7-4aea-966e-28d6585a2b7a_1160x433.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260505214253_71b078ab-86d7-4aea-966e-28d6585a2b7a_1160x433.png\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/71b078ab-86d7-4aea-966e-28d6585a2b7a_1160x433.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:433,&quot;width&quot;:1160,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:118630,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/196586628?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd8fd3e48-1415-4d42-a41c-c2b34a3542bb_1178x500.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;a